Inside, the SPR314LOS features LED lighting to provide an attractive display when the door is opened. This unit utilizes automatic defrost to reduce user maintenance. The dial thermostat is located inside to prevent unsupervised temperature changes. With its compact size and weatherproof construction, the SPR314LOS is an ideal choice for restaurants with outdoor seating, bar counters, hydration stations, and other areas in need of reliable refrigeration in an easy fit.

311185911.Title: Summit Appliance 24 in. 5.5 cu. ft. Commercial Refrigerator in Black
311185911.Description: Sized under 24 in. wide and deep, the SCR600BGL offers a generous 5.5 cu. ft. of storage capacity. The user-reversible door features double pane tempered glass for added protection, with a brushed aluminum finish on the frame. The factory-installed front lock is located towards the top of the door for easier access. This unit comes with a black cabinet finish and is designed for freestanding use. Inside, the SCR600BGL includes four adjustable glass shelves for spill-proof storage and a half-sized wire shelf ideal for holding bottles in place. Automatic defrost ensures minimum user maintenance and a dial thermostat makes it simple to manage the temperature. This unit features an interior light operated with an On/Off rocker switch and a white interior finish to ensure optimum product visibility. Our unique "hidden" evaporator is located in the rear wall to help protect the unit's system and maximize shelf space. An internal fan helps to ensure the interior is more evenly cooled from top to bottom. The SCR600BGL is ETL-S Listed to NSF-7 commercial standards. Built-in capable and ADA compliant choices are also available.
